# Mentor Request Controller Endpoints
# Base URL: http://localhost:3001
# Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

### Create mentor request (protected)
POST http://localhost:3001/mentor-requests
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

{
  "mentorId": "<mentor-id>",
  "position": "Frontend Developer",
  "targetCount": 2,
  "reason": "Need more capacity for new project"
}

### Get all mentor requests (protected)
GET http://localhost:3001/mentor-requests
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

### Get mentor request by ID (protected)
GET http://localhost:3001/mentor-requests/{{id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

### Update mentor request (protected)
PATCH http://localhost:3001/mentor-requests/{{id}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

{
  "status": "APPROVED"
}

### Delete mentor request (protected)
DELETE http://localhost:3001/mentor-requests/{{id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}
